    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a mechanical M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry performs as intended. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and VANOS system inspection. A mechanically honest specimen that balances raw performance with legendary E46 ergonomics.",
